'''宫颈息肉'''（{{lang-en|cervical polyp}}）是一种常见的原发型息肉或肿物，通常生长于{{le|子宫颈管|Canal of the cervix}}表面<ref name="PAP">{{cite book
  | last =Boon
  | first =Mathilde E.
  |author2=Albert J. H. Suurmeijer
  | title =The Pap Smear
  | publisher =Taylor & Francis
  | date =1996
  | pages =87
  | url =http://books.google.com/?id=umcl4R3sp2AC&pg=PA87
  | isbn =3-7186-5857-7 }}</ref>。

并发原因不明，但与[[宫颈炎|宫颈炎]]相关<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Cervical Polyps
 |publisher   = Doncaster and Bassetlaw Hospitals ([[National_Health_Service|NHS]])
 |url         = http://www.dbh.nhs.uk/Library/Patient_Information_Leaflets/WPR22220-Cervical%20Polyps.pdf
 |format      = [[PDF|PDF]]
 |accessdate  = 2007-10-21
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20070207191644/http://www.dbh.nhs.uk/Library/Patient_Information_Leaflets/WPR22220-Cervical%20Polyps.pdf
 |archivedate = 2007-02-07
}}</ref>。慢性炎症长期刺激使宫颈管局部黏膜增生，子宫有排除异物倾向，使增生的黏膜逐渐自基底部向宫颈外口突出而形成一个或多个息肉<ref name="Medline">{{cite web
  | last =Smith
  | first =Melanie N.
  | title =Cervical polyps
  | publisher =[[MEDLINE|MEDLINE]]
  | date =2006-05-10
  | url =http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/001494.htm
  | accessdate =2007-11-05
  | archive-date =2012-07-10
  | archive-url =https://www.webcitation.org/693tEJ6eP?url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/001494.htm
  | dead-url =no
  }}</ref>，直径一般约为1厘米，红色呈舌形，质软而脆，易出血，蒂细长。根部多附着在宫颈外口，少数在宫颈管壁。宫颈息肉极少恶变（占少于1%）；然而部分子宫恶性肿瘤，偶尔也呈息肉样表现。在超声波或活检下，可以检查出宫颈息肉，通常采用手术方式切除<ref>{{cite web   | last =Moore   | first =Anne   | title =How Should I Treat Postcoital Bleeding in a Premenopausal Patient?   | publisher =Medscape.com   | date =2001-09-20   | url =http://www.medscape.com/viewarticle/412468   | accessdate =2007-10-21   | archive-date =2012-10-26   | archive-url =https://www.webcitation.org/6BhJ5IOpK?url=https://login.medscape.com/login/sso/getlogin?urlCache=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5tZWRzY2FwZS5jb20vdmlld2FydGljbGUvNDEyNDY4   | dead-url =no   }}</ref>，切除后通常不会复发<ref name="Medline" />。

